   9:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h **** /** @brief Non Volatile storage class for persistent settings on an external flash device.
  10:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****  *  @author shensley
  11:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****  * 
  12:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****  *  Storage occupied by the struct will be one word larger than 
  13:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****  *  the SettingStruct used. The extra word is used to store the
  14:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****  *  state of the data, and whether it's been overwritten or not.
  15:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****  * 
  16:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****  *  \todo - Make Save() non-blocking
