  24:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****     /** State of the storage. 
  25:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****      *  When created, prior to initialiation, the state will be Unknown
  26:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****      *  
  27:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****      *  During initialization, the state will be changed to either FACTORY,
  28:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****      *  or USER. 
  29:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****      * 
  30:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****      *  If this is the first time these settings are being written to the
  31:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****      *  target address, the defaults will be written to that location,
  32:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****      *  and the state will be set to FACTORY.
  33:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****      * 
  34:/Users/reza.kalfane/Workspaces/Daisy/DaisyExamples/libDaisy/src/util/PersistentStorage.h ****      *  Once the first user-trigger save has been made, the state will be 
